-- Gamesa Signs Agreement With Toyota on Electric Cars For Spain
-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 2012-04-24T09:24:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/gamesa-signs-agreement-with-toyota-on-electric-cars-for-spain.html
Gamesa Corp. Tecnologica SA signed
an agreement with  Toyota Motor Corp. (7203)  to promote the use of
electric cars in  Spain , the company said in an e-mailed press
release.  Gamesa will test a plug-in Toyota Prius to analyse the cars
performance and study the charging infrastructure that it will
require.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Sills at 
 bsills@bloomberg.net  